{"id":1735132,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:16.398Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735132,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Syurgaku Tak Sempurna","overview":"# My Imperfect Paradise  The story tells of two best friends born into wealthy families, Tengku Zarif (Shah Iskandar) and Fariena (Uqasha Senrose), who grow apart when Zarif decides to marry a village girl named Zalia (Raja Ilya). Their happy marriage is struck by tragedy when they lose their child in an accident, causing Zalia to suffer emotional trauma. The situation becomes even more difficult when Zalia discovers that as a result of the accident, she can no longer have children. Tengku Zarif's mother, Tengku Zaharah (Didie Alias), asks her son to marry his childhood friend Fariena, who eventually gives Zarif a son. Zalia's disappointment leads her to decide to move to Yogyakarta to ease her suffering and plan to win Zarif back. In a cruel manner, Zalia orchestrates an accident that leaves Fariena paralyzed. Finally, Zalia manages to return to the man she loves.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/nOqKpN2dHTI5WSpYTSaStvLdCIT.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2017-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Syurgaku Tak Sempurna","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1428946,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Raja Ilya","original_name":"Raja Ilya","popularity":0.1972,"profile_path":"/5kx3hrY2VubyaSy3MAGf8G5UAYz.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5eca3444d1340c8ce2f84d","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1824723,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Shah Iskandar","original_name":"Shah Iskandar","popularity":0.5488,"profile_path":"/l2SDE3zb0Awyx3MXrzeWj86